  "text": "Finally, CePa can generate an informative report in HTML format through report() function. The report includes tables and figures that fully describe the results of the analysis. Additionally, pathways can be visualized interactively by Cytoscape Web [CITATION_1] in the report. An example of the report can be found at http://mcube.nju.edu.cn/jwang/lab/ soft/cepa/p53test/.",
